CS:GO VERSION
THIS IS A PORT OF A CSGO MAP I DID NOT CREATE THIS!



A map for the MAPEADORES ZOMBIE APOCALYPSE Mapping Contest!

Uptop an ancient mountain lies a Sanctuary of hope. Due to unforseen consequences, the holy land has been infected by a sinister plague.
Triggering the altar within the Sanctuary should be sufficient to wipe out the plague.

The map features:
-A beautiful marble castle to shoot zombies (or chop humans into bits!)
-Varied difficulty defense points
-Engaging zombie teleports to keep them in the action
-Souls-genre ambient music, matching the vibe of the map
-No bullshit, items, lasers or bosses. Just classic ZE gameplay!
